{"tid":936201,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友發生咩事？","createTime":"2018-12-10T14:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T16:48:19.000Z","uid":75707,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"eb67ebee71f8a9caef2b015427efb566f531bfad","tid":936201,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"女朋友以前唔會check我電話<br />\n自上星期經常借我電話玩 睇我電話<br />\n<br />\n咁耐以黎 有咩女仔搵我我都會同女朋友報告<br />\n女朋友都信任我 <br />\n就算知我手機密碼都唔會話去check我手機<br />\n但係呢個星期佢變到好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n經常睇我電話<br />\n問好奇怪既問題 例如 你會唔會有一日出去偷食<br />\n又係咁講 我知你始終有日會唔要我之類<br />\n<br />\n佢就不嬲都鍾意睇愛情片既<br />\n以前睇都係睇死港女鍾意睇既韓國戲<br />\n但我留意到佢呢個星期睇親都係講伴侶偷食 <br />\n聽親既歌都係講比伴侶背叛<br />\n<br />\n我女朋友發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打女朋友試過咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底佢諗緊乜"},{"pid":"6b676d174a6bcac4deed8de4fb89f3c00a8b2d2f","tid":936201,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經常睇我電話<br />\n問好奇怪既問題 例如 你會唔會有一日出去偷食<br />\n又係咁講 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我知你始終有日會唔要我之類</span><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6bd72633c504d71b28c4f4d752608d0935ca6c37","tid":936201,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b676d174a6bcac4deed8de4fb89f3c00a8b2d2f","tid":936201,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經常睇我電話<br />\n問好奇怪既問題 例如 你會唔會有一日出去偷食<br />\n又係咁講 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我知你始終有日會唔要我之類</span><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T14:48:45.000Z","msg":"佢話我會搵到個更加好更加靚既女仔就唔要佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2718e710e9baedbd67e6154f15b1c66e3de159f0","tid":936201,"uid":118271,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb67ebee71f8a9caef2b015427efb566f531bfad","tid":936201,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited